'''Ea Jansen''' (14 November 1921 – 20 April 2005) was a historian of [[Finno-Ugric people|Finno-Ugric]] [[history]] originally from [[Estonia]]. Until her death, she worked for the [http://www.tpu.ee/ Tallinn Pedagogical University].
[From an Ethnic Community to National Statehood: The Case of Estonians] - An article written by Jansen in 1998.
