{{Infobox person | name = Leonid Vasilyev | image = Leonid Vasilyev.jpg | imagesize = | caption = | birth_name = Leonid Sergeyevich Vasilyev | birth_date = {{Birth date|1930|10|9}} | birth_place = [[Moscow]], [[RSFSR]], [[Soviet Union]] | death_date = {{Death date and age|2016|10|6|1930|10|9}} | death_place = [[Moscow]], [[Russia]] | othername = | yearsactive = | spouse = | website = | notable role = }}'''Leonid Sergeyevich Vasilyev''' ({{lang-ru|Леони́д Серге́евич Васи́льев}}; October 9, 1930, [[Moscow]] — October 6, 2016, Moscow<ref>[https://www.hse.ru/news/life/192756130.html Умер Леонид Васильев]</ref>) was a Soviet and Russian historian, social scientist, religious scholar, sociologist, orientalist (sinologist)<ref>[https://www.livelib.ru/author/312117-leonid-vasilev Леонид Сергеевич Васильев] // livelib.ru</ref> and [[Doktor nauk|Doctor of Historical Sciences]].<ref>[http://www.friends-partners.org/partners/orient/persons/vasilyevls.htm Леонид Сергеевич Васильев — Friends and Partners]</ref>
Vailyev was Head of the Laboratory of Historical Research and HSE ([[National Research University – Higher School of Economics]])<ref>[http://onlinefilm-hd.com/load/serialy/vozvrashhenie_1_sezon_2005/1-1-0-1751 Биографическая справка]</ref> and until 2011, Head of the Department of General and National History and a professor.<ref>[http://www.liberal.ru/seminars/cat/4296 Факторы, способствующие и препятствующие модернизации: современные и традиционные культуры, взгляд историка]</ref> He began his tenure as the head of the sector of Theoretical Problems of the History of the East, then the Department of Oriental History of the [[Institute of Oriental Studies of the Russian Academy of Sciences]] and finally, the Institute's chief research officer.
He authored works devoted to the history and culture of China, the problems of Oriental studies and universal history - including the theory of the historical process - and the driving forces and dynamics of evolution.<ref name="интервью">[http://politics.ntu.edu.tw/RAEC/act02.php Интервью Л. С. Васильева]</ref><ref>[http://viperson.ru/people/vasiliev-leonid-sergeevich Рейтинг элиты России]</ref> Among these works is a two-volume university textbook, ''History of the East,'' a six-volume textbook series on ''Universal History'', monographs on the problems throughout ancient Chinese history, a textbook, ''History of Eastern Religions,'' and other books.<ref>[http://abhidharma.ru/A/Raznoe/0043.pdf История религий Востока]</ref> == Basic work == * Agrarian Relations and the Community in Ancient China (11th-7th centuries BC) (1961)<ref name="интервью" /> *Cults, Religions, Traditions in China (1970); 2nd edition (2001) * Problems of the Genesis of Chinese Civilization. Formation of the Foundations of Material Culture and Ethnicity (1976) * Problems of the Genesis of the Chinese State (1983) * History of Eastern Religions (1988)<ref>[http://flibas.space/a/19025 Леонид Сергеевич Васильев // Флибуста]</ref> *Problems of the Genesis of Chinese Thought. Formation of the Foundations of Worldview and Mentality (1989) * History of the East in 2 volumes (1993) * Ancient China in 3 volumes<ref>[http://www.koob.ru/vasilyev_leonid/ Леонид Васильев. Книги онлайн]</ref> ** Prehistory, Shan-Yin, Western Zhou (until the 8th century BC). (1995) ** Chunqiu Period (8th-5th centuries BC) (2000) ** The Zhangguo Period (5th-3rd centuries BC) (2006) * East and West in History (Basic Parameters of Problematics) // Alternative ways to civilization (2000) *Evolution of the Society. Types of the Society and their Transformation (2011) * Universal History in 6 volumes (2012-2013)<ref name="интервью" /> * History of Religions (2016) ==References== {{reflist}}
